Package: mylinear
Type: Package
Title: Simple Linear Regression Model Package
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yilin Yan
Maintainer: yilinyan@umich.edu
Description: This package provides a simple implementation of a linear regression model. It includes a function to estimate the slope and intercept of a linear model given a set of predictor and response values. It is designed as an educational tool to help users understand the basics of linear regression modeling in R.
